Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长本事了 连德西尔也死在你手里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最大的错误就是自投罗网
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是大魔头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这么说也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你的 X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往哪跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人品也用光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为骑士 不会对战友见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉甘 这里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先修理损毁级别低的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人没剩多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 你这么激动有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候最重要的就是斗志 斗志！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么要牵连柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是牺牲了一个人 少在那鬼哭狼嚎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不该上战场！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的家乡 许多人死得更一文不值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那样 也不是牵连柚铃理由！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把柚铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把柚铃还来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧装填弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修理用的后备部件不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从受损严重的机体身上拆来用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完了 半吊子X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 UE！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 还要拼刺刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面就是要塞司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样半路就会变成马蜂窝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器 全部投降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开通往动力炉的闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开通往动力炉的闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别费力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人不惧死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们想像成四头八手的外星人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论长得怎么样 也不是人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害死无辜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈… 柚铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是被你们杀的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收起枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了武器就相互杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球人果然够原始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 亚库·多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚库·多勒 就是那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎还有人认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以黑市商人亚库·多勒的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把武器情报泄漏给地球圈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱发了多起内乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在调查你们UE的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还发现了另一则有关亚库·多勒的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:11:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,14年前 「天使陨落」事件发生的当天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被摧毁的卫星 天使附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个男人在宇宙中被救起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你把机动战士引导进卫星天使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它们发动了袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知那是一座没有任何联邦军事设施的和平乐土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星天使上有我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那上面有我的一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为复仇而来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了亲手杀死你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇 就为了这么无聊的感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可悲的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们又是为了什么在战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的大义？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你们称呼为UE的… 我们的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及人类那段被诅咒的历史！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特那家伙 到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,150年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类过度增长的人口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过了地球可以容纳的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 政府祭出了火星移民计划「Mars Birthday」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星…移民计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球联邦开始实验性的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在火星圈建造起了十六座殖民卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并让部分人移居到了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年火星圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他们认为是一片广阔富饶的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 事实证明他们错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星磁力风暴引发的不治之症
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致了20%的移民罹难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是发生在火星圈的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划宣告失败
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终未能阻止疾病的蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移民全部死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有大批人被遗留在火星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球联邦为隐瞒自身在勘测方面的失职行为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,割弃了留在火星圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人在与恐怖绝症抗争的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为重返地球 这唯一的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在火星圈建立起了属于自己的新兴国家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们 「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「维甘」…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是UE的真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球圈自由自在生活着的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听见我们痛苦的呐喊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们渴望重返家园的灵魂的呐喊声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们就可以破坏殖民卫星…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走众多无辜者的生命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们发动的不过是一场报复战争
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说也就是复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 错了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是这么低次元的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些凡夫俗子理解不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不可能理解！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又…那又怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论出于什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会原谅你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢 因为你们根本不是人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果有这种觉悟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们根本无法与之对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目的 注定终将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 必须被实现！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们… 化作灵魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也同样可以回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您…是这样说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于可以…回地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 这警报难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的地球人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫 古鲁迪克·艾诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死你父亲的 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被复仇的亡灵缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此踏上自己悲剧的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里快爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 歌姬号 撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE的要塞 在分崩离析…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他们终于成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子 干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归根结底竟然是人类间的互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争还会持续下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多半…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我歇一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来 一事无成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没能保护好柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么成为救世主保护大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为击败UE 我要成为救世主！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场以攻击UE藏身据点为目的的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对宇宙要塞安巴德发动的突袭作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事后被称为「驱蝠战役」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球圈激起了轩然大波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我威胁歌姬号主干乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强行推动了作战实施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我个人的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而后 古鲁迪克舰长主动揽下违反军纪的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为叛逃者开始了狱中生涯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管是他的行动 揭开了UE的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且取得了巨大战果…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是叛逃者？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 地球联邦政府对外宣称
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是联邦军总司令部下令实施了此次作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相再次被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同150年前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩盖失败的火星移民计划时那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知是那次愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:21:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造就了眼前的这一切…
